OL,6,FA hammer-wielding burglar from
OL,7,FNottinghamshire who attacked a
OL,8,Fpensioner has been jailed.
OL,10,FConnor Cooper forced his way into the
OL,11,FNewark home of a "vulnerable" man on
OL,12,F28 January.
OL,14,FThe 22-year-old smashed his way
OL,15,Fthrough a bedroom window and knocked
OL,16,Fthe victim to the floor.
