OL,3,CHammer-wielding burglar broke into
OL,4,Chome and attacked pensioner
OL,6,FThe victim, who struggles to walk, hit
OL,7,Fhis head as he fell to the floor.
OL,8,FCooper, who was wielding a claw
OL,9,Fhammer, then kicked the man in the
OL,10,Fribs and chest and threatened to kill
OL,11,Fhim if he moved.
OL,13,FAt the time of the incident, Cooper
OL,14,Fwas already part of the police's
OL,15,FIntegrated Offender Management (IOM)
OL,16,Fscheme to prevent such offending.
OL,18,FThe scheme targets prolific offenders
OL,19,Fwho commit a disproportionate level of
OL,20,Fcrime across the city and county.
