OL,6,FCooper denied he was involved in the
OL,7,Fburglary and said he was jogging
OL,8,Fthrough the area.
OL,10,FHowever, detectives were able to use
OL,11,Fprecise GPS tag data to place him at
OL,12,Fthe scene, which showed Cooper leaving
OL,13,Fthe property and climbing over a
OL,14,Fgarden fence before deciding to remove
OL,15,Fthe electronic tag.
OL,17,FCooper subsequently went on the run
OL,18,Fbefore being arrested in South
OL,19,FYorkshire.
