OL,6,FAppearing at Nottingham Crown Court on
OL,7,F25 March, Cooper, of Parliament Court
OL,8,Fin Newark, was convicted of burglary
OL,9,Fof a dwelling with intent to steal and
OL,10,Fjailed for four years.
OL,12,FSergeant Rebecca Jepson, of
OL,13,FNottinghamshire Police's IOM team,
OL,14,Fsaid: "Cooper's unacceptable behaviour
OL,15,Fhas caused distress to homeowners and
OL,16,Fblighted local communities.
OL,18,F"Despite denying his involvement, we
OL,19,Fwere able to track him down via
OL,20,Fconditions enabled by the IOM
OL,21,Fprogramme and bring Cooper to justice.
