OL,6,F"It is important that we work closely
OL,7,Fwith our partner organisations to
OL,8,Freduce the reoffending of prolific
OL,9,Findividuals, to create safer
OL,10,Fcommunities across Nottinghamshire.
OL,12,F"The reasons for offending can be
OL,13,Fcomplex, but we are committed to
OL,14,Fprotecting our communities from harm,
OL,15,Fand by addressing these causes
OL,16,Fdirectly, we can reduce victims of
OL,17,Fcrime and costs to the criminal
OL,18,Fjustice system.
